    "description": "Long Running Job Failure incident on the Customers pipeline (RTL_CUS_LRJF): warehouse slotting-optimization batch fails on secret expiry.",
    "symptoms": "Nightly warehouse slotting-optimization DAG fails after 4h at the final MinIO upload step with an authentication error.",
    "root_cause": "The MinIO service-account access key rotated automatically (90-day policy) but the Airflow connection's Secret was not updated in the secrets manager sync job.",
    "business_impact": "Optimized slotting plan for next-day picking not published; warehouse operates on a 2-day-old plan, reducing picking efficiency.",
    "resolution": "Rotate and update the MinIO credential in the Airflow connection; add a credential-expiry pre-check sensor at DAG start rather than failing 4 hours in."
  },
